Version 0.6.0 (2021-02-07)
--------------------------
Fix Vagrant build environment (#114)
Add ability to template the name of a step in a Factotum DAG (#113)
Add ability to template the name of a Factotum DAG (#117)
Update Copyright years to 2016-2019 (#115)
Ensure raw factfile is templated to allow webhooks to work (#118)
Fix failing tests on Rust 1.40.0 (#120)
Bump hyper to 0.10.+ to support OpenSSL 1.1 (#119)
Target Ubuntu Trusty for Linux builds (#122)
Append tags to the environment so as to make them available to sub-processes (#121)
Migrate to Git Actions and remove Bintray (#124)
Update Copyright years to 2016-2021 (#125)

